Class NavigationControllerForInstructor

java.lang.Object
com.Software.FitnessSystem.InstructorPageNavigation.NavigationControllerForInstructor
public class NavigationControllerForInstructor extends Object
Handles navigation for the instructor pages in the fitness system. This class is responsible for controlling the flow between different instructor pages by displaying the current page and executing the corresponding action based on the user's choice. It uses the Page class to manage individual page displays and actions.
Author:
Ammar Shafii

  • Method Details

    • navigateTo

      public void navigateTo(Page page, InstructorPageControllers controller)
      Navigates to a specific page and allows the instructor to interact with the page. Continuously prompts the user to enter a choice and executes the selected option. This method runs in an infinite loop, allowing the instructor to interact with the page until they exit the program.
      Parameters:
      page - The page to navigate to.
      controller - The controller responsible for managing admin page actions.
